    <h2>Who runs it</h2>
    <p class="muted">ArtempireMJ is founder-run. Morris Javan built it to do one thing well, to tell
      the world through the artists who live it, and he keeps the eye steady from behind the work.
      When he appears in it, it is as one maker among the many the institution covers. The artists
      carry the story. He makes sure it gets told.</p>

